New Trier vs. Maine South #17 New Trier(6-0) takes on Maine South(4-2) in a Central Suburban South showdown.

Second Quarter | Watch this play at The Cube • Play made score: 14 New Trier – Maine South 9

Second Quarter | Watch this play at The Cube • Play made score: 14 New Trier – Maine South 16
• Brian Collis buys himself time before finding Matt Holbrook in the back of the endzone!
